  "message": "fuzz(evidence-ledger): add 16 structured corpus seeds\n\nCoverage expansion for fuzz_repair_evidence_ledger harness:\n- Event types: CorruptionDetected, RepairAttempted/Succeeded/Failed,\n  ScrubCycleComplete, PolicyDecision, WalRecovery, TransactionCommit,\n  TxnAborted, VersionGc, SerializationConflict, FlushBatch\n- Edge cases: empty input, whitespace-only, invalid JSON lines\n- Boundary values: u64::MAX timestamps, u32::MAX block groups,\n  full-range block_range tuples\n- Multi-record JSONL sequences\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
